354
00:21:06,651 --> 00:21:07,485
<font color="japanese">（教団兵）フン</font>

355
00:21:07,568 --> 00:21:10,446
<font color="japanese">見せしめには ちょうどいいか</font>

356
00:21:15,451 --> 00:21:17,245
